<text evidence="5">Inhibited by tert-butyl 4-(3-thiophen-2-yl-1,2,4-oxadiazol-5-yl) piperidine-1-carboxylate (RF1) and 1-(thiophen-2-ylacetyl)-4-(3-thiophen-2-yl-1,2,4-oxadiazol-5-yl)piperidine (RF3).</text>
